{
  "stem": "13981.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they supplied us with the affidavits to be able to get the whole family into the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother was-- my mother's trip was delayed by about a year and a half or two because she was in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had undergone a lung operation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she was in Switzerland at the time, and-- but she joined us later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so long ago, I-- my-- I had some relatives in Berlin, also a brother of my mother, who did all the paperwork because the consulate was there, and everything was-- all I know is that we only went to the consulate once and were interrogated a little bit, and then we got our papers.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember that I didn't know where Bernalillo was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] No idea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1935.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how long the process took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were quotas already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it took a little time, though.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in-- we left in December 1935, spent Christmas and New Year on the high seas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went through the Panama Canal and landed in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the part of the trip I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Elbe, the German river, Elbe, was the name of the ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, I really, at that time, was already on the farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had no particular-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wasn't homesick or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad, though, I remember, cried when he was aboard the ship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But us kids didn't have that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that particular [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE] feeling about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
